    <a href="#2025%e5%b9%b4%e9%81%a5%e6%84%9fai%e5%89%8d%e6%b2%bf%e8%ae%ba%e6%96%87%e8%a7%a3%e8%af%bb%e5%9f%ba%e7%a1%80%e6%a8%a1%e5%9e%8b%e4%b8%8e%e8%bd%bb%e9%87%8f%e7%ba%a7%e6%a3%80%e6%b5%8b" class="header-mark"></a>2025年遥感AI前沿论文解读：基础模型与轻量级检测</h1><blockquote>
